Package acme.exams.exceptions

  • Exception Summary 
    Exception Description
    DateAlreadyUsed
    Exception thrown when is added an exam in a date in which another exam has already been set
    DuplicatedEnrollmentIdException
    Exception thrown when is added a student with a duplicated enrollementId
    DuplicatedUsernameException
    Exception thrown when is added a student with a duplicated username
    ExamIdAlreadyPresent
    Exception thrown when is added an exam with a duplicated id
    ExamNotFoundException
    Exception thrown when an exam is not found
    InvalidContentException
    Exception thrown when invalid content has been provided in input by the user
    InvalidDateException
    Exception thrown when an invalid date has been provided by the user
    InvalidDateSequenceException
    Exception thrown when is created an exam with registration date before the exam date
    MarkNotFoundException
    Exception thrown when is not found the mark for a student
    MaxStudentsReachedException
    Exception thrown when adding a student to an exam and the maximum number of students has been already reached
    NotUniqueExamForDateException
    Exception thrown when are added multiple exam for the same day
    UserNotFoundException
    Exception thrown when a user is not found given a username and a password
